 chosen learning rate and\ncommunication rounds. It is noteworthy that our analysis is feasible for\nnon-IID clients.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 7 Aug 2022 04:17:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-09"}
